INQUIRE FOR MORE DETAILS

Priano is the country’s most sought-after exclusive interiors space. The Design Center spans over 20,000 square feet, Priano is equipped with a Commercial Library, Executive Offices, Conference Space, Private Studios, Luxury Steam Shower, Live Kitchen Vignettes, Custom Closets & Window Treatments, Design Layout Space, and Presentation Displays.

BECOME A MEMBER

TRADE MEMBER BENEFITS

 Priano serves as the pinnacle of the Greater Tampa Bay design community. Redefining the luxury design process you provide your clients, through access to centralized resources, exclusive products, tech-centric selection sheets, private studios, community events, and trade bonuses. Priano’s trade programs were strategically crafted to streamline & elevate the design process, enabling Builders, Designers, and Trade Professionals to increase profitability and save time. 

CENTRALIZED RESOURCES

Design, work, and gather at Priano a curated and centrally sourced design center with a dynamic mix of co-working, executive offices, conference rooms and event space.

TRADE BONUSES

Our trade bonus program was built by the trade for the trade. Your trade member portal will allow you to seamlessly manage your projects, margins (up to 10%), and selections digitally.

PRIVATE STUDIOS

Our private studios provide the perfect space to elevate your client's experience and maximize productivity. Fully Furnished. High Speed Internet. Screen Mirroring. Presentation Wall. Seats 4-8 Persons.

DIGITAL SELECTION SHEETS

Our proprietary software has digitized the way you select, manage, and share your project selections. All trade memberships have access to their own member portal and digital selection sheets.

Conference Space

Gorgeous 10 person 2nd floor conference room that is sure to "wow" your clients. Available with select trade memberships.

DISPLAY ISLANDS

Get hands on with your clients leveraging our display island and presentation walls to build their home live.

PRESENTATION WALLS

Light up your selections and place them on our "build-your-home" presentation walls. Walls are located throughout the showroom.

COMMUNITY EVENTS

Community programming is an integral part of our Priano Trade Program. In addition to member-sponsored events, we host a mix of fun events.

PRIVATE OFFICE

Gorgeous 2nd-story office fully furnished with custom chairs, cabinetry, storage, and desk space.

PREMIUM OFFICE

Want to have a design studio inside of Priano? Check out our state-of-the-art smart home studio that doubles as a studio space.

HOSPITALITY BAR

Treat yourself and your guests to our fully stacked hospitality bar. Snacks, Sparkling Water, Nespresso, and More!

EXCLUSIVE CEU EVENTS

Priano curates events throughout the year specific to continued education credits for its Trade Members.

MAIL SERVICE

Trade Members Mailbox Service can be purchased as an add-on service.

BECOME A MEMBER
